data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! **Highly Motivated Sellers** Welcome to 1461 Buchanon Dr! A charming 2 story home on a scenic creek lot with a formal dining room, finished office space in the basement, large bedrooms with big closets, lots of storage space and an over sized garage with room for a workshop. Located minutes to I-24, shopping, dining, entertainment and Fort Campbell. Curtains, home security cameras, and Trampoline will not convey.
